44:14.836 --> 44:17.211
Well, lucky there's not a horse
with that name in the race...

44:17.336 --> 44:19.211
- 'cause we'd bet on him.
- Oh, no, no, no.

44:19.336 --> 44:21.627
I mean, my attorney friend
would take that under advisement.

44:21.627 --> 44:23.919
- Mm-hmm.
- I got exclusive rights to that name.

44:24.003 --> 44:26.128
All right, all right,
all right. Yeah.

44:26.128 --> 44:28.128
So let me ask you
a question.

44:28.128 --> 44:30.919
Are you ever frightened that when a guy
comes over your house and pays you...

44:31.003 --> 44:33.919
that he's gonna maybe,
like tie you up and kill you?

44:34.003 --> 44:36.420
Oh, no. I always
get paid in advance.

44:36.502 --> 44:39.211
- Come on.

44:39.295 --> 44:41.502
- Eager Beaver. He's paying.
